'''Përparim Daiu''' (born 21 April 1970) is a retired [[Albania]]n footballer who has served as head coach of several clubs in the [[Albanian Superliga]].

==Club career==
Daiu played the majority of his career for [[Besa Kavajë]] and [[Partizani Tirana]].

==International career==
He made his debut for [[Albania national football team|Albania]] in an August 1995 [[friendly match]] away against [[Malta national football team|Malta]] and earned a total of 4 caps, scoring no goals. His final international was a January 1998 friendly against [[Turkey national football team|Turkey]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://eu-football.info/_player.php?id=24234|title=Player Database}}</ref>

==Managerial career==
After retiring as a player, Daiu went into coaching and was in charge of hometown club Besa (two spells), Shkumbini (also twice) and Tomori. In January 2012 he took the reigns at [[KF Laçi|Laçi]] for a second time as well.<ref>[http://www.panorama.com.al/sport/perparim-daiu-eshte-trajneri-i-ri-i-lacit/ Përparim Daiu është trajneri i ri i Laçit ] - Panorama {{sq icon}}</ref> In February 2013 he returned to Besa for a third time as coach.<ref>[http://www.panorama.com.al/prezantohet-daiu-besa-do-mbijetoje/ Prezantohet Daiu: Besa do mbijetojë] - Panorama {{sq icon}}</ref>

